import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col, Button } from 'react-bootstrap'

export default function Filtrado() {
    return (
        <Container style={{display: "flex",  margin: "0px auto"}}>
            <Row>
                <Col>
                <Button style={{ margin: "5px"}}>
                        Condicion
                    </Button>
                </Col>
            </Row>       
            <Row>
                <Col>
                <Button style={{ margin: "5px"}}>
                        Mayor Precio
                    </Button>
                </Col>
            </Row>       
            <Row>
                <Col>
                <Button style={{ margin: "5px"}}>
                        Menor Precio
                    </Button>
                </Col>
            </Row>            
        </Container>
    )
}
